Equipment/tools used to create and run Return to Polygon.

Computer setup equipment:
- Raspberry Pi 3 Model B+
- Monitor with HDMI cable
- Keyboard with USB connection
- Mouse with USB connection
- SanDisk Ultra microSDHC UHS-I card with adapter
- Raspberry Pi Universal Power Supply (2.5A, 5.1V)

Camera setup equipment:
- Raspberry Pi Camera V2

LED matrix setup equipment:
- GST60A05-PJ1 Adaptor (6A, 5V)
- Universal power cord (i.e. with C13 female connector)
- RGB Matrix Bonnet for Raspberry Pi
- RGB LED matrix (64x32 - 6mm pitch)
- GPIO ribbon cable
- LED matrix power cable

Paint setup equipment:
- Terumo 5mL luer lock syringes (at least 5)
- Acrylic paint (cyan, magenta, yellow, white, black - or combinations that can achieve these colours)

